gui.textual

Interface Colors

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Textual

    interface Colors
    Interfaces
    Holds the default ANSI Escape Colors, supported in Unix-alike shells and others.

    It is used in the Textual interface for implementing prints with colors.

    Author:
    Renato Cordeiro Ferreira
    See Also:
    Textual
